      "contents": "<div class=\"markitup-box\">\n<b>《反叛的鲁鲁修》，里面描述了这样的一个中国：</b><br/>\n<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvNzg4M2FkNzZjNGQ1ZjUwZjQ1Zjk0LnBuZz93aWR0aD01ODcmaGVpZ2h0PTQwNQ\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/7883ad76c4d5f50f45f94.png?width=587&amp;height=405\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/7883ad76c4d5f50f45f94.png?width=587&amp;height=405\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/7883ad76c4d5f50f45f94.png?width=587&amp;height=405\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvZjc5YzE2NzRhODdkZGQwNjBkOGMwLnBuZz93aWR0aD01NTUmaGVpZ2h0PTk4\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/f79c1674a87ddd060d8c0.png?width=555&amp;height=98\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/f79c1674a87ddd060d8c0.png?width=555&amp;height=98\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/f79c1674a87ddd060d8c0.png?width=555&amp;height=98\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvY2ViNGJkYjE0YWYxN2Q1NTBiMGY3LnBuZz93aWR0aD00ODcmaGVpZ2h0PTEyMQ\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/ceb4bdb14af17d550b0f7.png?width=487&amp;height=121\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/ceb4bdb14af17d550b0f7.png?width=487&amp;height=121\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/ceb4bdb14af17d550b0f7.png?width=487&amp;height=121\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvZTQ0MjU3MTE0NmY0MjBlMzBjYzI4LnBuZz93aWR0aD01OTYmaGVpZ2h0PTExOA\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/e442571146f420e30cc28.png?width=596&amp;height=118\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/e442571146f420e30cc28.png?width=596&amp;height=118\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/e442571146f420e30cc28.png?width=596&amp;height=118\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvNWYxZDMwNmMwODkzNWVkMmYxZGYwLnBuZz93aWR0aD03MDImaGVpZ2h0PTExMA\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/5f1d306c08935ed2f1df0.png?width=702&amp;height=110\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/5f1d306c08935ed2f1df0.png?width=702&amp;height=110\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/5f1d306c08935ed2f1df0.png?width=702&amp;height=110\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<br/>\n<b>当时看到这感觉到很有冲击力，心里想（怎么可以这样说中国！），实际上（已经把现实的中国联想在一起了）</b><br/>\n<br/>\n<b>后来的剧情就是，统治阶级在危难之际卖国求荣，想润到不列颠（也就是美国）拿身份，看到这我真是笑死了，很难不想到中共。</b><br/>\n<br/>\n<b>结果这帮宦官的内部对话被全国公开，引发了超越六四的事件（后来我就想，假如中共内部也有一些不见得人的对话被录音公开出去，会发生什么呢？）</b><br/>\n<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvNWY5NDQzNjgwMDc0OTQ2MzQ5OGY4LnBuZz93aWR0aD02ODImaGVpZ2h0PTgy\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/5f94436800749463498f8.png?width=682&amp;height=82\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/5f94436800749463498f8.png?width=682&amp;height=82\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/5f94436800749463498f8.png?width=682&amp;height=82\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvODljMDExZTg4OTcxYTQ3MjY3ZTUxLnBuZz93aWR0aD01MzEmaGVpZ2h0PTc3\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/89c011e88971a47267e51.png?width=531&amp;height=77\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/89c011e88971a47267e51.png?width=531&amp;height=77\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/89c011e88971a47267e51.png?width=531&amp;height=77\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<b><a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvNGU5YThkZDI2MDA1NTljMjQ0MGIzLnBuZz93aWR0aD0zNjEmaGVpZ2h0PTkz\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/4e9a8dd2600559c2440b3.png?width=361&amp;height=93\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/4e9a8dd2600559c2440b3.png?width=361&amp;height=93\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/4e9a8dd2600559c2440b3.png?width=361&amp;height=93\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a></b><br/>\n<b><a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvYmY0NTQ2ZTM5ODM5ZGFkYzE2YmNiLnBuZz93aWR0aD03ODMmaGVpZ2h0PTU0Nw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/bf4546e39839dadc16bcb.png?width=783&amp;height=547\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/bf4546e39839dadc16bcb.png?width=783&amp;height=547\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/bf4546e39839dadc16bcb.png?width=783&amp;height=547\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a></b><br/>\n<b><a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvZWFlYzA5NTlhNmE1MDdhMzk0NTIwLnBuZz93aWR0aD05NjMmaGVpZ2h0PTYxMg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/eaec0959a6a507a394520.png?width=963&amp;height=612\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/eaec0959a6a507a394520.png?width=963&amp;height=612\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/eaec0959a6a507a394520.png?width=963&amp;height=612\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a></b><br/>\n<br/>\n<b><a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvNTY1MmYzNmJmMTNmNDQ2OGUxZjU0LnBuZz93aWR0aD04OTEmaGVpZ2h0PTYwMA\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/5652f36bf13f4468e1f54.png?width=891&amp;height=600\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/5652f36bf13f4468e1f54.png?width=891&amp;height=600\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/5652f36bf13f4468e1f54.png?width=891&amp;height=600\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a></b><br/>\n<b>（用坦克打人民，这真的很经典）</b><br/>\n<b><a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvYWJiNTFiZTA5NTU4ZjcwZThkMTNmLnBuZz93aWR0aD05MDgmaGVpZ2h0PTU4Nw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/abb51be09558f70e8d13f.png?width=908&amp;height=587\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/abb51be09558f70e8d13f.png?width=908&amp;height=587\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/abb51be09558f70e8d13f.png?width=908&amp;height=587\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a></b> </div>",
