      "contents": "<div class=\"markitup-box\">\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvYmE1MmI0YWE2M2Q4MDc0ZTNkZDEwLnBuZz93aWR0aD0xMDM5JmhlaWdodD01ODU\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/ba52b4aa63d8074e3dd10.png?width=1039&amp;height=585\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/ba52b4aa63d8074e3dd10.png?width=1039&amp;height=585\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/ba52b4aa63d8074e3dd10.png?width=1039&amp;height=585\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvOTk0MzZjZTIxY2IyYzRhOThhZjkwLmpwZz93aWR0aD02MDAmaGVpZ2h0PTYwMA\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/99436ce21cb2c4a98af90.jpg?width=600&amp;height=600\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/99436ce21cb2c4a98af90.jpg?width=600&amp;height=600\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/99436ce21cb2c4a98af90.jpg?width=600&amp;height=600\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<br/>\n我以前同时在看这两种，真是造成价值观的极度混乱\t\t</div>",
