      "contents": "<div class=\"markitup-box\">\n\t\t\tPhineas and Ferb<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvYzM0MTU4ZWM0NWE3MGU3ZDkzNDY4LnBuZz93aWR0aD00NzImaGVpZ2h0PTM3Mw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/c34158ec45a70e7d93468.png?width=472&amp;height=373\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/c34158ec45a70e7d93468.png?width=472&amp;height=373\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/c34158ec45a70e7d93468.png?width=472&amp;height=373\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<br/>\nBen 10<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvYjBhY2UwMDBjMDJjMGY2YWY2YjgyLnBuZz93aWR0aD00NjUmaGVpZ2h0PTMzNg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/b0ace000c02c0f6af6b82.png?width=465&amp;height=336\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/b0ace000c02c0f6af6b82.png?width=465&amp;height=336\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/b0ace000c02c0f6af6b82.png?width=465&amp;height=336\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<br/>\nDespicable Me(this is a film series though)<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvMTdkZDJkMWJhYzQ5NDAxODM3YjRhLnBuZz93aWR0aD00MzgmaGVpZ2h0PTU5NA\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/17dd2d1bac49401837b4a.png?width=438&amp;height=594\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/17dd2d1bac49401837b4a.png?width=438&amp;height=594\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/17dd2d1bac49401837b4a.png?width=438&amp;height=594\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<br/>\nJackie Chan Adventures<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvZDM3Njk0NDk3NGYxZmM3MDM4OThlLnBuZz93aWR0aD00NzEmaGVpZ2h0PTI4NQ\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/d376944974f1fc703898e.png?width=471&amp;height=285\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/d376944974f1fc703898e.png?width=471&amp;height=285\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/d376944974f1fc703898e.png?width=471&amp;height=285\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<br/>\nGarfield<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvZDBmMTc5NjM4MTJjNjcyOTFkZWI2LnBuZz93aWR0aD0yODMmaGVpZ2h0PTQwMA\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/d0f17963812c67291deb6.png?width=283&amp;height=400\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/d0f17963812c67291deb6.png?width=283&amp;height=400\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/d0f17963812c67291deb6.png?width=283&amp;height=400\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<br/>\n在这里面，对我影响最大的是Phineas and Ferb，它鼓励我相信自己能做到一切，我是个天才！它添加了燃料对于我成为科学家的梦想，现在我在数学行业从事工作，有时到数学与自然科学的交叉领域作出贡献；以及它告诉我，我得打破传统和规矩，做一个会想象的人。\t\t</div>",
